name: Jill Stingray (+3 Costume LoRAs)| Va-11 Hall-a
description:
Jill Stingray from Va-11 Hall-a

Update 2.0 - MAJOR OVERHAUL and NEW FORMAT
TO DOWNLOAD THE INDIVIDUAL LORA PLEASE CHECK THE SEPARATE VERSIONS AT THE TOP

Ive long been getting complaints that my models would often have elements bleed between keywords, however I enjoy the convenience of prompting the outfit in a single keyword, so in order to combat this while retaining that convinience I am experimenting with a new delivery format for characters

Features the primary character LoRA and 3 separate costume LoRAs

The primary is only trained on the character and should be used for undefined outfits and can be combined with the costume LoRAs to get their canonical appearances

The costumes do not include the character training and could theoretically be used on any character LoRA

Primary LoRA Keyword: Jill

Costume LoRA's Keywords:
JillBartender
JillMagical
JillShirt

Please let me know in the comments if this works for you and I may go back and update all my Character LoRAs in this fashion (Even though it takes like 3 times as long 😅)

Recommend 0.8-1 Strength

If you've enjoyed my models, consider leaving a tip.
https://ko-fi.com/leontalon

"JillShirt" - Jill's casual home wear outfit
